                            <comment id="492364" author="adilger" created="Fri, 3 Apr 2026 01:01:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Charlie.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="492323" author="colmstea" created="Thu, 2 Apr 2026 14:12:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve updated the env configuration values for subtest-change sessions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
{
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;master&quot;&lt;/span&gt;  =&amp;gt; [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ONLY_MINUTES=30&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;HONOR_EXCEPT=y&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SLOW=yes&quot;&lt;/span&gt;],
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b_es6_0&quot;&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ONLY_MINUTES=30&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;HONOR_EXCEPT=y&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SLOW=yes&quot;&lt;/span&gt;],
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b_es7_0&quot;&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ONLY_MINUTES=30&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;HONOR_EXCEPT=y&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SLOW=yes&quot;&lt;/span&gt;],
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ONLY_REPEAT=10&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;HONOR_EXCEPT=y&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SLOW=yes&quot;&lt;/span&gt;]
}&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The change is effective on all new sessions so retests will pick up the change. Re-building is not necessary.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
